{"tid":1740961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對準焦點，勿阻民生","createTime":"2019-11-20T06:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T06:43:15.000Z","uid":292534,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f0fa34284749704f21be010b9456f8c9c4e6f564","tid":1740961,"uid":292534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:34:18.000Z","msg":"小弟住沙田，見晚上間中有14-15歲青年係屋村 堵路，之後送頭，我可以講話係送頭，因為效果不大 只係影響到夜晚收工既市民，之後又比狗捉。<br />\n阻到本身大量和理非出入 但對政府管治一點作用都冇影響。最近聽好多中年朋友都話好擾民民意逆轉，其實RB係未應該出返主幹 同市區做先有效果，而唔係為做而做？<br />\n<br />\n實際上 其實中環，尖咀，紅磡，金鐘<br />\n市區先係重點 同真正影響到遊客 ，核心管治同權力集中地，金鐘 中環 除左lunch有人行1-2個鐘之外 好似獨善其身咁，有時好唔明 香港好似黎巴亂咁 但股樓仲高企？<br />\n實際上示威行動係唔係只攬炒到民生而攬炒唔到班既得利益者？<br />\n<br />\n利申：有做家長，支持示威者所有決定 ，只理性討論"},{"pid":"6be53f185ce13451c0131d9771194cdfb8ab02a5","tid":1740961,"uid":65353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"聽日都有<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YSQjoYd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYSQjoYd.png&h=aa270dea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8af63faf7d65c65607d1d874253ce013a3177cd3","tid":1740961,"uid":292534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6be53f185ce13451c0131d9771194cdfb8ab02a5","tid":1740961,"uid":65353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"聽日都有<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YSQjoYd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYSQjoYd.png&h=aa270dea&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:53:25.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"e35b886b844fa9c9d86e68782590884ce89a73ca","tid":1740961,"uid":36994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:04:12.000Z","msg":"朝朝塞, 班藍絲好快會習慣"},{"pid":"474db87b9a2a6987ff07418e6e64e04cb14c118e","tid":1740961,"uid":292534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:43:15.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}